    "The model's robust performance on unseen data, evidenced by minimal percentage changes in RMSE and MAE between training and test sets, highlights its ability to handle various patterns and anomalies.",
    "Additionally, its integration of a classifier and extreme value indicator significantly enhances its accuracy in predicting rare and significant events.",
    "In future, it is interesting to investivate TXtreme for multivariate time series forecasting data, enhancing forecasting accuracy by capturing interrelated dependencies among multiple variables.",
    "Additionally, developing a unified transformer architecture that integrates LSTM, feed-forward neural networks along with specialized attention mechanisms tailored for extreme value forecasting would further enhance the model's sensitivity to critical patterns associated with extreme values.Fig. 11Fig.",
